337
00:16:03,298 --> 00:16:04,966
I don't know.
That sounds like a big project.

338
00:16:04,966 --> 00:16:08,553
Not a bigger project than moving,
you know? It would add square footage.

339
00:16:08,553 --> 00:16:10,513
