364
00:17:17,497 --> 00:17:22,459
Uh... [chuckles] ...but I was just
justifying bad behavior, you know?

365
00:17:22,459 --> 00:17:23,795
Um, as much as we fought,

366
00:17:24,295 --> 00:17:27,799
