379
00:18:00,081 --> 00:18:02,500
- Yes. Oh, good. Perfect. <i>"R" for Rando.</i>
- [laughing]

380
00:18:03,919 --> 00:18:09,591
- Whoa. Gummies are starting to hit.
- Hey. Those gummies be hittin', yo.

381
00:18:09,591 --> 00:18:11,551
