403
00:19:09,776 --> 00:19:10,777
Uh...

404
00:19:12,904 --> 00:19:14,364
Yes, it sounds like a good plan.

405
00:19:15,323 --> 00:19:16,324
Thank you.

406
00:19:18,285 --> 00:19:19,536
- Morning.
- Morning.

407
00:19:19,536 --> 00:19:21,371
