414
00:19:38,805 --> 00:19:41,099
That way, you can divide and conquer.

415
00:19:41,099 --> 00:19:43,018
Ooh, I like that.

416
00:19:44,561 --> 00:19:45,604
- He's good.
- Mmm.

417
00:19:45,604 --> 00:19:48,315
