- Yep. Yeah.

420
00:19:53,194 --> 00:19:56,281
Love it. Well, adieu. Get it?

421
00:19:57,198 --> 00:19:58,992
- ADU?
- Oh, ADU.

422
00:19:58,992 --> 00:20:03,538
- [chuckling] I do. I do.
- I do. Hey, you do get it.

423
00:20:04,789 --> 00:20:06,666
