444
00:21:05,100 --> 00:21:06,560
- It's nothing.
- What... It's something.

445
00:21:06,560 --> 00:21:08,562
- It's not.
- [stammers] It is clearly something.

446
00:21:08,562 --> 00:21:12,148
- What the fuck is going on?
- Okay, look, I can't tell you.

447
00:21:12,148 --> 00:21:14,484
This is intel from Katie.
Sylvia told her in confidence,

448
00:21:14,484 --> 00:21:16,319
and I can't air my baby's shit out.
That is what it is.

449
00:21:16,319 --> 00:21:18,780
- It's too late! You've already told me.
- I have not told you.

450
00:21:18,780 --> 00:21:20,240
- You've betrayed your baby!
- I haven't.

451
00:21:20,240 --> 00:21:22,033
- Your baby's been betrayed. Tell me.
- She hasn't.

452
00:21:22,033 --> 00:21:23,493
I'm your baby.

453
00:21:24,077 --> 00:21:25,787
